Module kivakit.resource
Package com.telenav.kivakit.resource.spi

Interface ResourceFolderResolver

All Superinterfaces:
Broadcaster, Listener, Mixin, NamedObject, Receiver, Repeater, RepeaterMixin, Transceiver, Transmitter
All Known Implementing Classes:
Folder.Resolver, Package.Resolver
public interface ResourceFolderResolver extends RepeaterMixin
A service provider interface that resolves ResourceFolders (including Packages and Folders). If the accepts(ResourceFolderIdentifier) method returns true, then this resolver can resolve the given ResourceFolderIdentifier with a call to resolve(ResourceFolderIdentifier). ResourceFolderResolverServiceLoader iterates through implementations of this interface provided by Java's ServiceLoader class and resolves ResourceFolderIdentifiers by calling accepts(ResourceFolderIdentifier) to find a resolver that can resolve the identifier.
Author:
jonathanl (shibo)
